overview: Rachel joined notifymd in 2001 and brings over 10 years of experience in financial reporting and budgeting. Before joining notifymd, she served as an auditor for KPMG, working with healthcare, banking, and non-profit clients. Rachel began her career doing budgeting and bookkeeping for the Admissions and Registrars office at Murray State University. She also received a Bachelor of Science degree in Accounting from Murray State University.
